data.description: Motivated sellers, seller will consider all offers! Welcome home to the pristine Hodges Bayou Plantation Gated Community. This home features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths on a corner lot! The main bedroom is large with a separate soaker tub and shower and water closet, features an enormous closet. The open concept in the living room, dining room and kitchen areas features 8-foot ceilings. There are blinds on every window for privacy. The 8 foot island in the kitchen will allow 5 chairs comfortably and the pantry is in the perfect place for all the storage you need. Stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen features touch screen refrigerator, and this is a smart home with Kwik Set Keyless entry, Skybell doorbell, Echo Dot device, Quolsys touch panel controls lighting, thermostat, front door and more. Split bedroom plan, with the 3 kids or guest bedrooms on the opposite side of the home from the main bedroom This property is only 2 years old!! Fantastic buy.. All measurements are approximate, if important buyer can verify measurements.
